  "home.intro.asraBody": "Spirit Realm's Ambassador are composed of tens of thousands of ordinary humans spread across various countries and ethnic groups around the world. Association members all possess the special power to remotely control attached spirits (ghosts) via the Internet (Power of Remote Controlling Attached Spirit (ghost) --- PRCASG); they are also tasked with the mission of revealing the truth of the Spiritual World to all of humanity.",
