  "home.truth.abstractBody": "As the founder of ASRA, Woos family filmed a series of three-season documentaries of Woos ethereal life and world for over 1,400 minutes. This documentary is the first time in human history to systematically explore and reveal the truth of soul, life, world and governor with a large amount of evidence",
