  "home.truth.s2.description": "This documentary provides the evidence of spirits and ghosts existing while people are alive and after death from scientific perspective and how it cause illness to the physical body. The organs, physiological systems, and basic pathology of spirits.It contains four parts: 1. Evidence of the existence of spirits ghosts and the general situation of their existence. 2. Physiology of human spirit soul 3. Pathology of human spirit soul 4. Physiology and pathology of spirits ghosts",
  "home.truth.s2.season": "SEASON 2",
